 * 
 * This test program is to test pmp_ok() when share mode (RW=01).
 * Based on other test cases for mseccfg stiky bits, this test expects following:
 * - RW = 01. For RW != 01, less combinations to show it fail.
 * - MML set
 * - Regine matched.
